trong>IIT</strong><strong>
</strong><strong>Madras</strong><strong> Chennai 600036</strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: justify;"><strong>Professor Steffen Leonhardt</stro=
ng><strong><sup>1</sup></strong><strong> of RWTH Aachen, Germany</strong> i=
s visiting IIT Madras to deliver a course under the GIAN<sup>2</sup> initia=
tive of Government of India. Dr. V.
 Jagadeesh Kumar and Dr.&nbsp;Boby George (host faculty at IIT Madras for t=
he GIAN program) will coordinate this event.</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <sup>=
1</sup> <a href=3D"https://www.medit.hia.rwth-aachen.de/en/institute/team/"=
